Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.64,0:00:21.45,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找尋著看不見的明天 著急地用手觸摸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.60,0:00:25.95,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而受傷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.10,0:00:38.51,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來是沒有出口的迷宮 就像需要解謎的拼圖一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.20,0:00:49.77,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使沒有奇蹟出現  夢想也將成為勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.01,0:00:54.94,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feel your Heart  在荏苒的季節中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.09,0:00:57.86,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你的憧憬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.01,0:01:00.36,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just my Love  因為那份思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.51,0:01:03.69,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我了無形的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.93,0:01:09.77,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像稍微感受到了迷惘和煩惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.77,0:01:11.33,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論在什麼時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.48,0:01:14.75,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feel your Heart  在荏苒的季節中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.49,0:01:23.63,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just my Love  對你的思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.63,0:01:28.64,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feel your Heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.48,0:19:56.75,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love is burning 在心中綻放的玫瑰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.90,0:20:03.58,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在黑暗中燃盡  僅是一束火焰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.87,0:20:12.26,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在滿是隔閡的街上 如遊戲般的迷失自我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.39,0:20:16.51,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以小丑的心情躊躇著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.35,0:20:24.85,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要踐踏悲傷的殘片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.97,0:20:29.19,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人在未來中戀愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.77,0:20:37.33,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以解開今晚的謎底仍然是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.61,0:20:41.87,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up！真面目  Hurry up！回到從前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.15,0:20:49.38,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love is passion　兩個人的手中充滿的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.50,0:20:56.39,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投入黑暗之中  想緊緊擁抱住陽光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.76,0:21:01.89,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love is burning 在迷宮中相互Kiss
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.01,0:21:10.94,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁向樂園  僅差一道門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.45,0:00:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨著時代的演繹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.95,0:00:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,困難的案件也與日俱增
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.75,0:00:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天新一終於出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.85,0:00:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但樣子有點奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.05,0:00:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.75,0:00:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.75,0:00:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻有著成人的頭腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.15,0:00:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.05,0:01:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然出現在大叔的偵探社的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.45,0:01:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關西高中生偵探服部平次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.75,0:01:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來好像要和我決一勝負
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.15,0:01:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個時候達村外交官的太太來到偵探社
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.55,0:01:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要調查兒子女友的品行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.65,0:01:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當我們去到他們家裏時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.85,0:01:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發現外交官被毒殺在書房裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.85,0:01:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且是密室殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.05,0:01:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,服部陸續地發現證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.05,0:01:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將密室謎題解開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.25,0:02:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼重要的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.45,0:02:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我卻因感冒和喝下服部所帶來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.35,0:02:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫作白乾兒酒的關係而發燒倒下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.35,0:02:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這次發燒卻非比尋常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.25,0:02:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像很不對勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.55,0:02:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好熱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.85,0:02:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心臟好像快要裂開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.05,0:02:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 工藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.85,0:02:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你對我的推理要是有意見的話就快點出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.35,0:02:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你再不出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.45,0:02:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件案子就要被我解開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.25,0:02:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外交官殺人事件(後篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.95,0:02:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 兇手是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.55,0:02:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兇手到底是誰 服部老弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.25,0:02:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別急 先等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.05,0:02:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 工藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.55,0:02:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道你放棄了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.95,0:02:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.95,0:02:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點 沒時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.05,0:02:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殺死被害人後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.15,0:02:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要完成這個手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.85,0:02:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少要五至六分鐘的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.15,0:02:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而犯案的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.95,0:02:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是從三點半到四點這三十分鐘內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.25,0:03:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醫生來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.95,0:03:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.15,0:03:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此四點的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.45,0:03:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我們一起回到這裏的達村太太就排除在外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.95,0:03:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同樣的在三點到四點這段時間內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.65,0:03:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站在大門口和附近的鄰居聊天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.65,0:03:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並迎接我們和達村夫人回到這裏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.45,0:03:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管家先生也是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.65,0:03:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你到哪裡去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.95,0:03:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此 在我們和達村夫人到達這裏之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.65,0:03:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在管家出來迎接夫人的這段時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.85,0:03:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死者的兒子和他女朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.85,0:03:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也曾經到二樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.95,0:03:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是頂多只有一、兩分鐘的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.55,0:03:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是不可能犯罪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.15,0:03:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底跑到哪裡去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.45,0:03:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.75,0:03:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.05,0:03:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到哪裡去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.55,0:03:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.95,0:03:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩點多的時候才到這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.45,0:03:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並且一直在書房隔壁的客廳看電視的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.85,0:03:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位老先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.05,0:03:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有你才有可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.75,0:03:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,證據就是我之前在和室裏發現的這根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.45,0:03:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用來綁住鐵針的釣線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.05,0:04:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種釣線是在新材料的釣線中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.75,0:04:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耐力最強最細的一種特殊的釣線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.55,0:04:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡釣魚 應該不會說你不知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.65,0:04:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.75,0:04:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我們和達村夫人要去書房的半路上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.75,0:04:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還在樓梯上遇到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.55,0:04:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你先到和室那邊等我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.05,0:04:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.45,0:04:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在行兇之後就到了和室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.05,0:04:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你確認了你自己的完美犯罪以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.05,0:04:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我在和室的垃圾桶裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.75,0:04:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻發現這根釣線就是不可動搖的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.95,0:04:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.15,0:04:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 有說錯嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.45,0:04:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.45,0:04:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問柯南有沒有到這裏來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.75,0:04:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.95,0:04:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.15,0:04:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.05,0:04:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.05,0:04:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.45,0:04:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把我的兒子阿勳殺死的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.65,0:04:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.65,0:04:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對 不是他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.75,0:04:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.65,0:05:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本不是他幹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.55,0:05:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.05,0:05:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.55,0:05:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.55,0:05:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這人就是工藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.15,0:05:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工藤新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.15,0:05:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.55,0:05:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.65,0:05:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.35,0:05:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底到哪裡去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.55,0:05:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以為你不見了 你又突然出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.95,0:05:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.85,0:05:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我有多擔心嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.55,0:05:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 你哭什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.65,0:05:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.75,0:05:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說得沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.65,0:05:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你突然出現說不是他幹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.75,0:05:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是說我的推理都說錯了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.85,0:05:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先等一下 小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.25,0:05:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好多汗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.75,0:05:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.35,0:05:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.85,0:05:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.35,0:05:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是說說我的推理到底哪裡錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.55,0:05:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.45,0:06:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是說你剛才說的那個手法只是紙上談兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.75,0:06:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百分之百不可能做得到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.75,0:06:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.35,0:06:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工藤老弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.85,0:06:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要在這裏先插個嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.55,0:06:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他剛才對密室的手法推理得非常完美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.35,0:06:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且剛才我也用我的褲子做過實驗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.75,0:06:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們先用綁了鐵針的釣線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.75,0:06:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有綁鐵針的那一頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.05,0:06:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用膠帶固定在死者的鑰匙環上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.55,0:06:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再讓綁了鐵針的釣線那頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.05,0:06:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從我的長褲口袋內側通過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.45,0:06:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後再將這兩端握住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.05,0:06:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再一起走出書房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.75,0:06:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把門鎖上後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.95,0:06:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再用力抽取有針的那一頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.75,0:06:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那把鑰匙就會自己跑到口袋裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.95,0:06:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個時候再用力一拉的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.65,0:06:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,釣線就從膠帶上抽了出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.75,0:06:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來只要把釣線收好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.65,0:06:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,證據也就消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.95,0:06:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,密室的手法也因此完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.35,0:06:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問那把鑰匙真的跑進口袋了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.85,0:06:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目暮警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.25,0:06:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼聽起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.45,0:06:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那把鑰匙的確是跑進了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.25,0:07:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被害者的雙層口袋裏 是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.75,0:07:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.65,0:07:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要是不信的話就看清楚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.65,0:07:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看這個褲子的雙層口袋…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.25,0:07:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.05,0:07:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才明明已經讓釣線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.25,0:07:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從這個雙層口袋裏穿過的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.45,0:07:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為鑰匙進去的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.85,0:07:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目暮警官是坐著的緣故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.05,0:07:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.45,0:07:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為只要是坐著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.75,0:07:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,口袋就會折疊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.05,0:07:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阻礙到鑰匙進入口袋的通道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.85,0:07:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在鑰匙真的進入裏面的雙層口袋之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.35,0:07:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,釣線就會從膠帶裏被抽出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.35,0:07:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.95,0:07:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果被害人的體形和目暮警官差不多胖的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.85,0:07:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個情形就更明顯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.15,0:07:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.55,0:07:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得我把手伸到被害人的口袋的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.85,0:07:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.65,0:07:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,褲子還鼓鼓的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.75,0:07:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個很可能有萬一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.55,0:07:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 十次裏至少會有一次巧合吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.85,0:07:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再做幾次都是一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.95,0:07:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自己好好回想看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.75,0:07:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那把鑰匙在被害人的雙層口袋裏的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.95,0:07:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.45,0:08:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鑰匙的方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.95,0:08:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.05,0:08:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算鑰匙真的萬一跑進雙層口袋裏面去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.45,0:08:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也應該只有鑰匙環
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.75,0:08:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為在狹窄的雙層口袋裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.95,0:08:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鑰匙環跟鑰匙根本不可能被折成く字形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.15,0:08:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是鑰匙跟鑰匙環卻好好的進去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.55,0:08:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是說兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.85,0:08:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在一開始的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.55,0:08:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就把鑰匙放在死者的雙層口袋裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.25,0:08:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那你倒說說看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.75,0:08:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在和室找到的這根帶針的釣線又怎麼解釋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.45,0:08:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那只是兇手設下的一個陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.95,0:08:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為的就是把罪名嫁禍給這位老先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.65,0:08:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也找到五、六根同樣的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.75,0:08:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這個家裏到處都是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.05,0:08:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個兇手連和室以外的地方都設計到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.05,0:08:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以不管案發當時這位老先生在哪裡都脫不了關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.95,0:08:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 那位老先生自己都承認是他犯的罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.95,0:08:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為這位老先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.05,0:08:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是故意跳進這個兇手設的陷阱裏面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.55,0:09:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至於他是基於什麼原因我就不清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.95,0:09:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是這間書房是一間完全的密室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.05,0:09:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難不成你想說死者是自殺身亡的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.15,0:09:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對 他不是自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.05,0:09:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且兇手也留下了真正犯罪手法的線索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.65,0:09:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真正犯罪手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.05,0:09:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道你忘了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.35,0:09:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在發現被害人的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.05,0:09:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這間書房裏正播放著歌劇音樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.05,0:09:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且被害人的面前還堆了一疊書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.05,0:09:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,播放歌劇 是兇手在刺毒針的同時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.15,0:09:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了消除被害人可能發出的慘叫聲做的準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.05,0:09:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,書則是為了死者被刺的時候可能產生的痛苦表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.95,0:09:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所做的掩飾工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.65,0:09:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.55,0:09:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兇手這麼費心到底要遮掩誰的耳目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.05,0:09:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於這個 服部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.35,0:09:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.45,0:09:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.15,0:09:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然不只是服部你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.65,0:09:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時和你一起進入這個書房裏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.45,0:09:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭或者毛利偵探注意到的話都會破壞他的計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.05,0:09:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說 難道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.15,0:09:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我肯定兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.65,0:10:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是進入書房後直接靠近被害人的那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.45,0:10:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 那個兇手就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.55,0:10:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 兇手…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.85,0:10:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫人 就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.75,0:10:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫人殺了老爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.15,0:10:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.95,0:10:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.45,0:10:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被害者還是活著的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.45,0:10:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.65,0:10:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一開始達村夫人只是用某種藥物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.15,0:10:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓外交官睡著了而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.95,0:10:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後達村夫人就在假裝叫被害人的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.45,0:10:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將毒針刺了進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.15,0:10:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時沒有人注意到其實也是很自然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.05,0:10:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為那種安眠藥的藥效很強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.95,0:10:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毒針上塗的又是劇毒的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.55,0:10:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被害者會在被刺後直接從睡眠狀態被毒死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.95,0:10:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,達村夫人之所以準備歌劇和那些書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.05,0:10:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為的只是預防萬一而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.75,0:11:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是那個安眠藥一旦從屍體裏被化驗出來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.75,0:11:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個手法就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.95,0:11:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒有人會知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.95,0:11:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們一直認為死者是在我們進屋前就死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.85,0:11:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以就會認為是兇手為了讓死者不反抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.55,0:11:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而事先讓他服下了安眠藥而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.85,0:11:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.25,0:11:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兇手刻意的把偵探找到這裏來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.25,0:11:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利用他們認為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.45,0:11:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會有人在他們面前殺人的這個盲點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.65,0:11:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進行心理性的密室殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.15,0:11:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是這樣吧 工藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.25,0:11:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然那樣的話你就拿證據出來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.95,0:11:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.35,0:11:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,達村夫人根本就沒有做出拿毒針的動作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.15,0:11:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 達村夫人進入房間的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.85,0:11:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確是在大家沒有注意的情況下自然的拿出了毒針
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.15,0:11:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和鑰匙一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.85,0:11:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鑰… 鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.55,0:11:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 達村夫人身上那把書房的鑰匙環
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.25,0:11:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟被害人身上的鑰匙環是同樣的設計
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.15,0:12:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 達村夫人的鑰匙環應該也能打開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.25,0:12:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 可以讓大家看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.25,0:12:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你手上的鑰匙環裏面的內容了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.05,0:12:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫人 可以請你讓我看一看嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.45,0:12:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個小槽是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.05,0:12:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據我推測 那個應該就是用來放置毒針的溝槽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.75,0:12:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她進入書房之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.25,0:12:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很快就把這根設置在鑰匙環裏面的毒針露了出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.65,0:12:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.25,0:12:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個有槽的鑰匙圈就是證明達村夫人是兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.35,0:12:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最有力也最直接的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.55,0:12:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這是為什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.05,0:12:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼達村夫人要殺死自己的丈夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.75,0:12:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我沒有猜錯的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.65,0:12:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的動機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.55,0:12:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該就在這張照片裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.65,0:12:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個不就是達村夫人年輕時的照片嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.95,0:12:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請再看清楚點吧 警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.85,0:12:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得這像誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.95,0:12:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟幸子小姐好像啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.95,0:12:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.25,0:13:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看除了髮色外幾乎完全一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.95,0:13:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們當然長得像了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.85,0:13:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.05,0:13:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幸子的母親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.05,0:13:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.25,0:13:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.65,0:13:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 幸子是你和外交官的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.35,0:13:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 幸子是我跟我前夫所生的女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.05,0:13:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 就是二十年前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.45,0:13:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被我現在的丈夫達村勳強冠上貪污的罪名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.45,0:13:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從社會上被抹殺的外交官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.05,0:13:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山城健二的親生女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.65,0:13:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山城健二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.25,0:13:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個十五年前死在牢裏的外交官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.95,0:13:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,達村真正的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.45,0:13:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是將那個時候和他同樣是外交官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.15,0:13:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻是競爭對手的山城拉下臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.85,0:13:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同時還可以把當時還是山城的妻子的我弄到手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.85,0:13:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我完全不知情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.05,0:13:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在山城被抓入獄後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.35,0:13:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幸子被親戚接走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.95,0:13:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時達村就對當時精神處於崩潰邊緣的我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.65,0:14:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是為了你才跟我老婆分手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.65,0:14:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就這樣輕易地上了達村的當
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.35,0:14:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始跟那個像魔鬼一樣的男人生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.15,0:14:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真正知道這整件事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.55,0:14:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在貴善把他女朋友幸子的照片帶回家來的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.15,0:14:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一開始我也以為只是跟她碰巧長得相像罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.85,0:14:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到達村他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.15,0:14:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能跟這個女的在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.05,0:14:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會讓那個男人的女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.25,0:14:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我的兒子在一起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.95,0:14:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我的懷疑之下忍不住詢問達村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.55,0:14:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在這個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.15,0:14:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就開始滔滔不絕的講起他陷害山城瀆職的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.35,0:14:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來我的公公當年也曾經幫助過他做這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.65,0:14:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 公江
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.15,0:14:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道我那個時候是怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.05,0:14:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.65,0:14:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你因為後悔當年所犯下的錯誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.25,0:14:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就自願跳進達村夫人設下的陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.15,0:14:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以剛才才會承認這件事是你做的 打算背下一切罪名吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.75,0:15:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今你現在再裝好人也沒用了 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.25,0:15:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山城因為被你們冠上莫須有的罪名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.75,0:15:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不明不白的死在牢裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.65,0:15:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貴善
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.15,0:15:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.95,0:15:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.55,0:15:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許沒有資格對你說這些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.95,0:15:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是幸子要拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.45,0:15:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.25,0:15:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.65,0:15:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,達村太太會對幸子小姐這麼凶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.25,0:15:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是不想被人家發現她們兩個人是母女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.95,0:15:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.95,0:15:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.45,0:15:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.45,0:15:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.35,0:15:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還好吧 新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.25,0:15:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是有點感冒而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.35,0:15:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你是怎麼把這整件事情弄得那麼清楚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.05,0:15:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你果然是在附近窺視
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.45,0:15:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡說 我是在電話裏聽那個戴眼鏡的小鬼說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.45,0:15:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.65,0:15:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.55,0:16:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說大阪那裏來了一個奇怪的偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.15,0:16:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我趕快趕回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.05,0:16:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所 所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.85,0:16:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上從另一個案子裏抽身坐電車趕了過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.65,0:16:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.55,0:16:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他已經跟我說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.45,0:16:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在電話裏頭沒問我好不好實在太奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.85,0:16:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的就在附近吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.35,0:16:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定就在這附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.35,0:16:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看著我擔心你的樣子就偷偷地笑我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.85,0:16:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.65,0:16:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你要這樣子對我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.75,0:16:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我是多麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.25,0:16:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.95,0:16:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不要傻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.55,0:16:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了 我是一個偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.65,0:16:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底好不好聽聲音就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.65,0:16:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新一 你等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.35,0:16:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就去叫醫生來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.55,0:16:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.55,0:16:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來我的推理從一開始的時候就弄錯了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.05,0:16:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次的比賽無論怎麼說都是我輸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.15,0:16:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是工藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.35,0:17:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的推理果然勝我一籌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.15,0:17:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.05,0:17:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,推理是沒有什麼輸贏或者上下的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.55,0:17:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.55,0:17:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真相永遠都是只有一個的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.95,0:17:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說得也對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.75,0:17:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來我的確太在乎勝負了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.05,0:17:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會不夠冷靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.05,0:17:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工藤 你真的只是感冒嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.35,0:17:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.55,0:17:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工藤 你不要緊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.35,0:17:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醫生 快點快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.85,0:17:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.05,0:17:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.25,0:17:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心臟又開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.45,0:17:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好熱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.45,0:17:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骨頭 好像快要融化似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.35,0:17:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.25,0:17:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道 我又要變回去了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.15,0:18:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才恢復了原狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.85,0:18:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在又要變回小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.65,0:18:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變回柯南了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.05,0:18:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.05,0:18:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.75,0:18:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼可以這樣子到處走動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.95,0:18:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是個病人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.95,0:18:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.05,0:18:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在變回柯南的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.35,0:18:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的身份就要被小蘭…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.05,0:18:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.65,0:18:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了 怎麼只剩下一件上衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.85,0:18:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.95,0:18:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託 不要那麼快變回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.25,0:18:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少讓我跟小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.45,0:18:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.95,0:18:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我親口對她說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.65,0:18:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用我的聲音對她說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.85,0:18:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少讓我和她再說一句話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.85,0:18:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.95,0:18:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裏傳來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.35,0:18:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.65,0:19:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.55,0:19:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到哪裡去了我到處找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.55,0:19:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有你這襯衫怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.65,0:19:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我流了很多汗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.85,0:19:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就從那個房間裏借了一件衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.45,0:19:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才有沒有看見新一啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.35,0:19:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新一哥哥的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.85,0:19:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說想起還有一件案子要處理就走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.55,0:19:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他剛才換了衣服就從大門那裏出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.45,0:19:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.55,0:19:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新一哥哥還說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.55,0:19:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於這一次是他破案的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.45,0:19:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望我們不要對任何人說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.85,0:19:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.25,0:19:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.65,0:21:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後我整整睡了三天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.75,0:21:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,服部平次也在這段時間回到了大阪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.55,0:21:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還好我在倒下之前交待過小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.45,0:21:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以在關於這次事件的報導上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.35,0:21:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有出現工藤新一的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.15,0:21:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣把我身體變小的那些黑衣人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.05,0:21:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不會知道我還活在這個世界上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.45,0:21:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我的身體在那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.65,0:21:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會突然變回高中生呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.05,0:21:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.75,0:21:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.35,0:21:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.35,0:21:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.35,0:21:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喝了他帶來的那瓶酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.75,0:21:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.15,0:22:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對錯不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.35,0:22:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是喝了那個酒身體才復原的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.05,0:22:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 看來這瓶酒還剩很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.95,0:22:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要喝一口就那樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.85,0:22:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我如果全部喝掉的話一定能完全復原了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.35,0:22:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.35,0:22:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在喝什麼啊柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.35,0:22:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是 竟然喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.85,0:22:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以的喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.25,0:22:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子怎麼可以喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.35,0:22:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 我已經高中二年級了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.45,0:22:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 高中生也還未成年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.25,0:22:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快去換衣服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.15,0:22:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的那些朋友來找你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.65,0:22:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.25,0:22:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.35,0:22:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼又是你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.85,0:22:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們好擔心你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.35,0:22:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到柯南你會因為感冒而請了三天假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.35,0:22:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊 可以不用去上學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.95,0:22:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也來感冒一下試試看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.75,0:22:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,元太你是絕對不會感冒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.25,0:22:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.25,0:23:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家不是都說傻瓜是不會感冒的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.75,0:23:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過太好了 你又跟原來一樣有精神了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.15,0:23:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我不幸又變回原來的樣子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.55,0:23:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我們非要一起到圖書館不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.55,0:23:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你沒有去上學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.75,0:23:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以現在班上沒交讀書報告的人就只有柯南你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.35,0:23:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們才想要去幫你寫報告 對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.15,0:23:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.55,0:23:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美陪我還可以
